function onLoad()
    MegaFreeze() -- Call MegaFreeze - Place it here so you can disable it by just commenting out this alone.
end

function MegaFreeze()
    local freezeByZone = {'4e6958'} -- Place GUIDs of script zones here
    local freezeByGUID = {'98f523', '79b304', 'b718b4', '316f83'} -- Place GUIDs of individual Objects here

    for _, obj in pairs(getAllObjects()) do
        if      obj.getName() == 'MegaFreeze' then
                obj.interactable = false
        elseif  obj.getDescription() == 'MegaFreeze' then
                obj.interactable = false
        else
            for _, guid in pairs(freezeByGUID) do
                if obj.getGUID() == guid then obj.interactable = false end
            end
        end
    end

     -- Freeze Objects by Zone
    for _, zone in pairs(freezeByZone) do
        for _, obj in pairs(getObjectFromGUID(zone).getObjects()) do
            obj.interactable = false
        end
    end
end

--[[
        It is best to use dynamic code, so using the Names or Descritions means you
        do not have to hardcore GUIDs. I just left that in as an example, as sometimes
        you need to retain names and/or descritpions for other parts of the scripts.

        You can of course add more seach criteria in the same was as the freezeByGUID
        to say MegaFreze by texture, or type or w/e.
]]

ObjectStates.LuaScript:
function onload()
    MakeButtons()
end

function func_Unfreeze()
    for _, obj in pairs(getAllObjects()) do
        if obj.interactable == false then
            obj.interactable = true
        end
    end
    MakeButtons('Freeze')

end

function func_Freeze()
    Global.call('MegaFreeze')
    MakeButtons('unFreeze')
end

function MakeButtons(switch)
    if switch == nil then
        self.createButton({
            label="Unfreeze Objects", click_function="func_Unfreeze", function_owner=self,
            position={0,0.5,1}, rotation={0,180,0}, height=900, width=2200,
            font_size=250,-- color={0,0,0}, font_color={1,1,1}
        })
    elseif switch == 'Freeze' then
        self.clearButtons()
        self.createButton({
            label="Freeze Objects", click_function="func_Freeze", function_owner=self,
            position={0,0.5,1}, rotation={0,180,0}, height=900, width=2200,
            font_size=250,-- color={0,0,0}, font_color={1,1,1}
        })
    elseif switch == 'unFreeze' then
        self.clearButtons()
        self.createButton({
            label="Unfreeze Objects", click_function="func_Unfreeze", function_owner=self,
            position={0,0.5,1}, rotation={0,180,0}, height=900, width=2200,
            font_size=250,-- color={0,0,0}, font_color={1,1,1}
        })
    end
end
